de.gematik.ti.healthcardaccess.cardobjects

Class FileControlParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.gematik.ti.healthcardaccess.cardobjects.FileControlParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICardItem

    public class FileControlParameter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICardItem

    The File Control Parameter is a set of control parameters, i.e., logical, structural and security attributes as listed in Table 12 from ISO/IEC 7816-4. Within the FCP, the context-specific class (first byte from '80' to 'BF') is reserved for file control parameters; tags '85' and 'A5' reference discretionary data.

    See Also:
    "ISO/IEC 7816-4"
